claim: West Nile fever is found in the region of the Americas surrounding the equator.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The specific neurological diseases that may occur are West Nile encephalitis , which causes inflammation of the brain , West Nile meningitis , which causes inflammation of the meninges , which are the protective membranes that cover the brain and spinal cord , West Nile meningoencephalitis , which causes inflammation of the brain and also the meninges surrounding it , and West Nile poliomyelitis -- spinal cord inflammation , which results in a syndrome similar to polio , which may cause acute flaccid paralysis .
